===Noun===
'''interrupt''' ([[interrupts]])

# {{italbrac|computing}} An event that causes a computer to temporarily cease what it was doing and attend to a condition
#: ''The '''interrupt''' caused the packet handler routine to run.''

====Translations====
computing: '''An event that causes a computer to temporarily cease'''
